    protected class RichDiagnosticFormatter.RichPrinter
extends Printer
    Enhanced type/symbol printer that provides support for features like simple names and type variable disambiguation. This enriched printer exploits the info discovered during type/symbol preprocessing. This printer is set on the delegate formatter so that rich type/symbol info can be properly rendered.

      • className

        protected String className(Type.ClassType t,
                           boolean longform,
                           Locale locale)
        从类复制的说明: Printer
        Converts a class name into a (possibly localized) string. Anonymous inner classes get converted into a localized string.
        覆盖:
        className 在类中 Printer
        参数:
        t - the type of the class whose name is to be rendered
        longform - if set, the class' fullname is displayed - if unset the short name is chosen (w/o package)
        locale - the locale in which the string is to be rendered
        返回:
        localized string representation
